metadata.name: SPACE AK
metadata.description:
SPACE AK47

What if AK-47 ,the most widely used shoulder weapon in the world since 1947, was also the most used weapon in multiverses?

We are bringing this fantasy into NFT world!
Travel between our 47 multiverses and discover each of these NFTs with their unique design.
There's a "HIDDEN MAZE" and a Golden key to pass the maze for the ones who travel 3 of the Multiverses .

To be continued...
